.TH DELPHI-BARCODE 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
barcode \- Generate 1D/2D barcodes
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbarcode\fR [\fB\-\-format\fR] [\fB\-\-height\fR] [\fB\-\-scale\fR] [\fB\-\-text\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIDATA\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate 1D/2D barcodes
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR \fI<FORMAT>\fR [default: code128]
Format: ean13, ean8, upca, code39, code128, codabar, code93, itf
.TP
\fB\-\-height\fR \fI<HEIGHT>\fR [default: 120]
Bar height in px
.TP
\fB\-\-scale\fR \fI<SCALE>\fR [default: 2]
Width scale (px per module)
.TP
\fB\-\-text\fR
Include human\-readable text below the barcode
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIDATA\fR>

